  id: 1
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD b\xE1c s\u0129 #1"
  category: 0
  content: "H\xF4m nay c\u0169ng nh\u01B0 nh\u1EEFng ng\xE0y kh\xE1c. B\u1EC7nh nh\xE2n
    th\xEC \u0111\xF4ng ngh\u1EB9t, thu\u1ED1c v\u1EABn ch\u01B0a c\xF3 ti\u1EBFn
    tri\u1EC3n g\xEC v\xEC ch\u1EB3ng ai mu\u1ED1n th\u1EED c\u1EA3. May th\u1EADt,
    c\xF3 th\u1EB1ng ng\u1ED1c n\xF3i mu\u1ED1n th\u1EED nghi\u1EC7m thu\u1ED1c \u0111\u1EC3
    c\xF3 ti\u1EC1n cho em trai n\xF3 \u0111i h\u1ECDc. Hmm, Ch\u1EC9 c\xF3 m\u1ED7i
    th\u1EB1ng n\xE0y l\xE0 ch\u1ECBu h\u1EE3p t\xE1c. C\xF3 l\u1EBD h\xF4m nay l\xE0
    ng\xE0y tr\u1ECDng \u0111\u1EA1i nh\u1EA5t \u0111\u1EDDi m\xECnh. B\xE1c s\u0129
    Edward."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
